sql: SELECT MIN(mc.note) AS production_note, MIN(t.title) AS movie_title, MIN(t.production_year) AS movie_year FROM company_type ct, movie_companies mc, title t WHERE ct.kind = 'production companies' AND mc.note not like '%(as Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer Pictures)%' AND t.production_year < 2006 AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id ;
